So then we can imagine this would be a

00:06:46.420 --> 00:06:48.660
literature assistant if we connect to

00:06:48.660 --> 00:06:51.700
online shoppers with blog articles or

00:06:51.700 --> 00:06:56.580
product reviews, then we can help these

00:06:56.580 --> 00:07:00.060
people to improve shopping experience

00:07:00.060 --> 00:07:02.900
so we can provide for example data

00:07:02.900 --> 00:07:05.095
mining capabilities to analyze the

00:07:05.095 --> 00:07:05.970
reviews to

00:07:06.020 --> 00:07:08.870
Compare products, compare sentiment of

00:07:08.870 --> 00:07:12.010
products and to provide a task support or

00:07:12.010 --> 00:07:14.010
decision support to help them choose

00:07:14.010 --> 00:07:15.370
what product to buy.

