Or we can connect the customer service

00:07:17.700 --> 00:07:21.560
people with emails from the customers.

00:07:22.320 --> 00:07:25.965
And we can imagine a system that can

00:07:25.965 --> 00:07:28.590
provide analysis of these emails to

00:07:28.590 --> 00:07:30.260
find the major complaints of the

