task support by automatically generating a response

00:07:37.640 --> 00:07:40.080
to the customer email, or maybe

00:07:40.080 --> 00:07:43.280
intelligently attach also promotion.

00:07:44.560 --> 00:07:47.430
Message if appropriate if the detector

00:07:47.430 --> 00:07:49.790
that's a positive message, not a

00:07:49.790 --> 00:07:51.330
complaint, and then you might to take

