he or she can expect the detailed

00:08:07.600 --> 00:08:09.240
response later, etc.

00:08:09.240 --> 00:08:12.890
All these are trying to help people to

00:08:12.890 --> 00:08:14.310
improve the productivity.

00:08:15.470 --> 00:08:17.720
So this shows that the opportunities

00:08:17.720 --> 00:08:20.590
are really a lot, it's just only

00:08:20.590 --> 00:08:22.136
restricted by our imagination.

00:08:22.136 --> 00:08:26.130
So this picture shows the trend of the

00:08:26.130 --> 00:08:28.650
technology and also it characterizes

00:08:28.650 --> 00:08:31.990
the intelligent information system in

00:08:31.990 --> 00:08:36.160
three angles you can see in the center

00:08:36.160 --> 00:08:37.620
there is a triangle that connects

00:08:37.620 --> 00:08:40.510
keyword queries to search and bag of

00:08:40.510 --> 00:08:41.495
words representation.

00:08:41.495 --> 00:08:44.290
That means the current search engines

00:08:44.290 --> 00:08:46.910
basically provides search support.

00:08:47.550 --> 00:08:52.090
Users and mostly model users based on

00:08:52.090 --> 00:08:53.170
keyword queries.

00:08:53.960 --> 00:08:57.940
And it sees the data through a bag of

00:08:57.940 --> 00:08:59.110
words representation.

00:08:59.110 --> 00:09:01.960
So it's a very simple approximation of

00:09:01.960 --> 00:09:04.580
the actual information in the

00:09:04.580 --> 00:09:05.320
documents.

00:09:06.060 --> 00:09:07.840
But that's what the current system

00:09:07.840 --> 00:09:08.380
does.

00:09:08.380 --> 00:09:11.340
It connects these three nodes in such a

00:09:11.340 --> 00:09:11.990
simple way.

00:09:11.990 --> 00:09:14.220
Or it only provides you basic

00:09:14.220 --> 00:09:16.923
search function and doesn't really

00:09:16.923 --> 00:09:18.620
understand the user.

00:09:18.620 --> 00:09:20.579
And it doesn't really understand it

00:09:20.580 --> 00:09:20.980
that much

00:09:20.980 --> 00:09:24.020
information in the documents.

00:09:24.020 --> 00:09:27.690
Now I showed some trends to push each

00:09:27.690 --> 00:09:28.300
node.

00:09:29.850 --> 00:09:32.280
Toward more advanced function, so think

00:09:32.280 --> 00:09:36.620
about the user node here so we can go

00:09:36.620 --> 00:09:37.950
beyond the keyword queries.

00:09:37.950 --> 00:09:40.050
Look at the user search history and

00:09:40.050 --> 00:09:43.020
then further model the user completely

00:09:43.020 --> 00:09:44.770
to understand the users task,

00:09:44.770 --> 00:09:48.560
environment, task need context or

00:09:48.560 --> 00:09:49.924
other information.

00:09:49.924 --> 00:09:53.730
So this is pushing for personalization

00:09:53.730 --> 00:09:55.836
and complete the user modeling and this

00:09:55.836 --> 00:09:57.620
is a major direction in research.

00:09:57.620 --> 00:09:59.845
In order to build intelligent

00:09:59.845 --> 00:10:00.980
information systems.

00:10:01.690 --> 00:10:03.640
On the document side.

00:10:04.320 --> 00:10:06.560
We can also see we can go beyond bag of

00:10:06.560 --> 00:10:08.810
words representation to have entity

00:10:08.810 --> 00:10:10.230
relation representation.

00:10:10.230 --> 00:10:13.170
This means we'll recognize peoples names

00:10:13.170 --> 00:10:16.520
their relations, locations etc and this is

00:10:16.520 --> 00:10:18.460
already feasible with today's natural

00:10:18.460 --> 00:10:20.480
language processing technique and

00:10:20.480 --> 00:10:23.240
Google's recent initiative on the

00:10:23.240 --> 00:10:24.340
Knowledge Graph.

00:10:24.340 --> 00:10:26.370
If you have heard of it, it's a good

00:10:26.370 --> 00:10:28.885
step toward this direction and once we

00:10:28.885 --> 00:10:31.400
can get to that level of representation

00:10:31.400 --> 00:10:34.220
in a robust manner at large scale, it can

00:10:34.220 --> 00:10:35.950
enable the search engine to

00:10:36.000 --> 00:10:38.640
provide much better service. In the

00:10:38.640 --> 00:10:39.400
future,

00:10:39.400 --> 00:10:41.810
we would like to have knowledge

00:10:41.810 --> 00:10:43.750
representation where we can add perhaps

00:10:43.750 --> 00:10:45.910
inference rules and then the search

00:10:45.910 --> 00:10:47.920
engine will become more intelligent.

00:10:49.170 --> 00:10:51.730
So this calls for large scale semantic

00:10:51.730 --> 00:10:54.470
analysis, and perhaps this is more

00:10:54.470 --> 00:10:56.180
feasible for vertical search engines.

00:10:56.880 --> 00:10:58.510
It's easier to make progress in a

00:10:58.510 --> 00:11:00.670
particular domain. Now on the service

00:11:00.670 --> 00:11:02.620
side, we see that we need to go beyond

