your knowledge that can be used in

00:11:38.690 --> 00:11:39.180
application

00:11:39.180 --> 00:11:41.193
or actionable knowledge that can be

00:11:41.193 --> 00:11:43.170
used for decision making. And

00:11:43.170 --> 00:11:45.270
furthermore the knowledge would be used

00:11:45.270 --> 00:11:48.530
to help user to improve productivity in

