finishing a task.

00:11:49.860 --> 00:11:51.965
For example, a decision making task.

00:11:51.965 --> 00:11:55.635
So this is a trend and so basically in

00:11:55.635 --> 00:11:57.350
this dimension we

00:11:58.000 --> 00:12:00.710
anticipate in the futur.

00:12:00.710 --> 00:12:02.230
Intelligent Information systems will

00:12:02.230 --> 00:12:05.350
provide intelligent and interactive

00:12:05.350 --> 00:12:05.820
task

00:12:05.820 --> 00:12:08.030
support. Now I should also emphasize

00:12:08.030 --> 00:12:10.025
interactive here because it's important

00:12:10.025 --> 00:12:13.420
to optimize the combined

00:12:13.420 --> 00:12:16.305
intelligence of the users and the

00:12:16.305 --> 00:12:19.432
system so we can get some help from

00:12:19.432 --> 00:12:23.000
users in some natural way and we don't

00:12:23.000 --> 00:12:24.670
have to assume the system has to do

