everything when the human user and the

00:12:27.600 --> 00:12:28.260
machine

00:12:28.310 --> 00:12:30.750
can collaborate in an intelligent way

00:12:30.750 --> 00:12:34.320
in an efficient way, then the combined

00:12:34.320 --> 00:12:36.770
intelligence will be high and in

00:12:36.770 --> 00:12:38.650
general we can minimize the user's

00:12:38.650 --> 00:12:41.250
overall effort in solving problem.

